@node Main "Squarado - Documentation"

                             'Squarado'  1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Squarado' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} played on an 8 by 8 tiles board.
The goal is to rotate bars so at least 3 bars are lined up in the
same direction, either horizontally or diagonally, as what is shown
on the bars.

  Oh, by the way: NEVER isolate bars...

  Have fun!

